                            <p>These can be provided face to face or virtually dependent on social distancing guidance at the time.</p>

                            <p>If you are interested in arranging an event for your group, please email the <a href="mailto:census.engagement@nisra.gov.uk">Census Engagement Team</a>.</p>
                            
